keyFacts: The invoice is dated November 1, 2002, and pertains to shipping services provided by FedEx.
Total charges for the services amounted to $37.08 after discounts.
Packages were dropped off on October 28, 2002, and delivered on October 31, 2002.
Darren Indyke and David Bagot are both identified as senders of the packages.
Kelly signed for the delivery of the packages.
